frames.caption: A woman in an elegant white and gold gown walks confidently down a cobblestone street, accompanied by a majestic eagle. The scene is set against the backdrop of ancient Roman architecture, including the iconic Colosseum.
frames.description: The image depicts a blend of modern fashion and ancient Roman elements, creating a surreal and regal atmosphere. The woman, adorned with a golden headpiece, exudes grace and power as she strides alongside the eagle.

frames.caption: A woman dressed in an elegant white gown stands confidently on a stone pathway, adorned with a golden crown and accessories. In front of her, a majestic eagle spreads its wings, poised as if ready to take flight. The background features a vast, open landscape under a clear sky.
frames.description: The scene depicts a regal and mythical setting, with a woman and an eagle positioned prominently in a natural, open environment. The atmosphere suggests a blend of elegance and power, enhanced by the woman's attire and the eagle's presence.
